name: SupabaseSaveState
shortDescription: Support to save game state to Supabase.
description: This extension adds support to save game state to [Supabase](https://supabase.com).
To set up the database, look [here](https://romw314games.w3spaces.com/wiki/gdevelop/supabase-save-state.html).

eventsFunctions.description: Call this before any other supabase actions or conditions.
eventsFunctions.name: SetupSupabase
